'''2020年印度旁遮普邦假酒事件'''發生於2020年7月下旬至2020年8月上旬，[[印度|印度]][[旁遮普邦|旁遮普邦]]至少有98人死于有毒的[[假酒|假酒]]<ref name="HT">{{Cite news|title=Death toll in Punjab hooch tragedy rises to 86; 7 excise officials, six cops suspended|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/chandigarh/death-toll-in-punjab-spurious-liquor-tragedy-rises-to-62/story-cRRu9MqeHlOjkcYR7FTxPL.html|accessdate=2 August 2020|work=hindustantimes.com|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111232130/https://www.hindustantimes.com/chandigarh/death-toll-in-punjab-spurious-liquor-tragedy-rises-to-62/story-cRRu9MqeHlOjkcYR7FTxPL.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=印度旁遮普邦假酒事件死亡人数升至98人|url=http://world.people.com.cn/n1/2020/0803/c1002-31807045.html|accessdate=|author=人民网|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405074703/http://world.people.com.cn/n1/2020/0803/c1002-31807045.html}}</ref>。仅在[[塔爾恩塔蘭縣|塔爾恩塔蘭]]地区就有63人死亡，其次是[[阿姆利则|阿姆利则]]，有12人死亡，[[古尔达斯普尔县|古尔达斯普尔]]有11人死亡。<ref name="HT" />警方在三个受影响的地区即阿姆利则农村、古尔达斯普尔和塔爾恩塔蘭进行了100多次搜捕，没收了假酒<ref name="BBC">{{Cite news|title=India toxic alcohol: Dozens die in Punjab poisoning|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/amp/world-asia-india-53624507|work=BBC|date=1 August 2020|accessdate=2020-08-03|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801174240/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/amp/world-asia-india-53624507|dead-url=no}}</ref>，至少有25人遭到逮捕。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Chauhan|first=Satender|title=Punjab hooch tragedy: 86 dead, 25 arrested so far, Rs 2 lakh ex-gratia for victims|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/punjab-hooch-tragedy-illicit-liquor-death-toll-arrests-accused-lakh-ex-gratia-amarinder-singh-top-developments-1706849-2020-08-01|accessdate=2 August 2020|work=indiatoday.in|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122062205/https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/punjab-hooch-tragedy-illicit-liquor-death-toll-arrests-accused-lakh-ex-gratia-amarinder-singh-top-developments-1706849-2020-08-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外還有7名税务官员和6名警官被停职<ref>{{Cite news|author=Ghazali|first=Mohammed|title=86 Dead From Punjab Toxic Liquor, 7 Excise Officials, 6 Cops Suspended|url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/number-of-deaths-in-punjab-spurious-liquor-tragedy-rises-to-62-2272662|accessdate=2 August 2020|work=ndtv.com|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124025919/https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/number-of-deaths-in-punjab-spurious-liquor-tragedy-rises-to-62-2272662|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=印度旁遮普邦假酒事件死亡人数升至98人|url=http://news.cctv.com/2020/08/03/ARTIGCcXFYvHKStMpJmMbqOh200803.shtml|accessdate=|author=CCTV|date=|format=|publisher=|language=}}</ref>。旁遮普邦政府为每名死者所在的家庭支付20万[[卢比|卢比]]撫恤金<ref>{{Cite web|title=死亡98人！快速火化 印度这起假酒案不简单|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2020/08-02/9254634.shtml|accessdate=|author=中國新聞網|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916170218/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2020/08-02/9254634.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

